Up to 5 years' experience;
Know-how in Azure OpenAI;
Experience in LangChain and other LLM management frameworks;
Knowledge of the use and deployment of Large Language Models (LLMs);
Experience in Prompt Engineering and Prompt Design;
Fluency in English (written and spoken).



